org.apache.cordova

类 LOG

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.cordova.LOG

  • public class LOG
extends java.lang.Object
    Log to Android logging system. Log message can be a string or a printf formatted string with arguments. See http://developer.android.com/reference/java/util/Formatter.html
